OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA chilly start for many then a
OL,6,Fdry day with plenty of sunshine, this
OL,7,Fturning hazy at times in the west.
OL,8,FFeeling quite warm in the afternoon
OL,9,Fwith light winds.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FA bright end to the day then
OL,12,Fa dry night with long clear spells.
OL,13,FBecoming chilly in the east with a
OL,14,Ftouch of frost and patchy fog.
OL,15,
OL,16,CFriday:FAnother dry and bright day
OL,17,Fwith long periods of sunshine. A
OL,18,Fchilly start then becoming quite warm
OL,19,Fby the afternoon. Some patchy mist may
OL,20,Faffect the east coast.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
